apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: yellow
spec:
  containers:
  - image: busybox
    name: lemon
    command:
      - sleep
      - "1000"
  - image: redis
    name: gold


    There are 3 common patterns, when it comes to designing multi-container PODs. 
    The first  : side car pattern. 
    The second : adapter 
    The third  : ambassador pattern.




